snippet.title: Celebrities That Exposed Amber Heard For Lying!
snippet.description:
These Celebrities Exposed Amber Heard For Lying In The Case Against Johnny Depp!

After years of being involved in different legal battles, it looks like Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard are finally getting close to the end of the big lawsuit. In the most recent development in Johnny's $50 million defamation case against Amber Heard, the actor’s legal team has issued subpoenas for Amber’s ex-boyfriend and technology king Elon Musk.
